<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.8.5">
<l>toḻunīr vaṭiviṉ kuṟaḷuruvāy vantu tōṉṟi māvalipāl</l>
<l>muḻunīr vaiyam muṉkoṇṭa mūvā vuruvi ṉammāṉai</l>
<l>yuḻunīr vayaluḷ poṉkiḷaippa vorupāl mullai mukaiyōṭum</l>
<l>kaḻunīr malaruṅ kaṇṇapurat taṭiyēṉ kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord of ageless form, coming and appearing in the form of a dwarf,</l>
<l rend="indent">with an appearance whose nature [all] worship,</l>
<l>Who once took the whole sea[-covered] world from Māvali,</l>
<l>I, his servant, saw for myself in Kaṇṇapuram where waterlilies blossom</l>
<l rend="indent">with jasmine buds at one side,</l>
<l>While in ploughed, watered fields, wealth abounds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
